{"customText":"

Hello! I'm Vladyslav Polishchuk.

At present, I'm a Full-Stack Software Developer at a progressive startup where we're pioneering a state-of-the-art website builder for developers. My role here allows me to indulge in my passion for React, as well as engage with the vibrant, innovative developer community that we serve.

"}

{"customText":"

But it's not all about coding for me. I'm equally drawn to pursuits like tennis, traveling, and snowboarding. I enjoy the thrill of a fast-paced game on the court, the awe-inspiring diversity of places and cultures around the world, and the exhilaration of descending snowy slopes. These activities not only bring balance to my life but also spark creativity and innovation in my work.

"}

{"customText":"

Outside of my primary job, I invest in promising companies on the stock market. The thrill of uncovering hidden gems and observing their growth mirrors my professional journey - where I started as a trainee and have since mentored numerous others to help them secure their first jobs in the industry.

"}

{"customText":"

Building for the web is what I love. Whether it's something as simple as a single HTML file or as complex as a large React application, the thrill remains the same. The web is a realm of boundless potential where anyone can be a developer, writer, or creator - there are no barriers, only opportunities. Just build, and the world is your oyster.

"}

{"customText":"

In the exciting realm of software development, there's always something new to learn, and I am committed to sharing my experiences and insights with the community. So, join me on this journey as we delve into the dynamic world of web development, investing, and beyond.

"}
